{"tid":2073420,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"初夏 －彩虹小隊致香港人公開信","createTime":"2020-06-21T10:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T17:04:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2a6264dd3cc1f0953c6632071fd6592a3a7873","tid":2073420,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A4%258F-%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%2599%25B9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Ywy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=bdf68b7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A4%258F-%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%2599%25B9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&h=d846a405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n【文：彩虹小隊】<br />\n<br />\n迎接初夏，一年過後「勇武」這兩字彷彿逐漸淡出人們的視線外。自反送中以來，香港人一直飽受著警暴等不公平待遇；哪裡有壓迫，哪裡就會有反抗。所謂「勇武」就在這此的社會壓力下誕生，一群又一群像我們這樣的香港人，決心走上街。"},{"pid":"967f361f17a031867d1682121e9baf45fb3fe4bf","tid":2073420,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[&darr;&darr;港獨強心針&darr;&darr;]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"e462847b99bf17a5098f32fc64ca9dae0179c9e1","tid":2073420,"uid":328890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a66ea002ab1609e372ece7a3ab2ac98e6299e75","tid":2073420,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93c0dc3cfc412be990c2ee74c5ef770e2703de5","tid":2073420,"uid":135277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"勿忘初心"},{"pid":"4960c48b14270f308bd76a69454de56b82ca38f9","tid":2073420,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2037e893f01a44a9198a2a29e61f195329b3f1e4","tid":2073420,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e462847b99bf17a5098f32fc64ca9dae0179c9e1","tid":2073420,"uid":328890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":